title: DuckTales Last 25 Episodes Complete Collection
description:
The last 25 episodes of the hit TV series DuckTales, which Disney has failed to release on DVD in a Volume 4.

Episode list (in chronological order by air date):
The Land of Tra-La-La
Allowance Day
Bubbeo & Juliet
The Good Muddahs
My Mother the Psychic
Metal Attraction
Dough Ray Me
Bubba's Big Brainstorm
The Big Flub
A Case of Mistaken Secret Identity
Blue Collar Scrooge
Beaglemania
Yuppy Ducks
The Bride Wore Stripes
The Unbreakable Bin
Attack of the Fifty-Foot Webby
The Masked Mallard
A DuckTales Valentine (Armour or Less)
Ducky Mountain High
Attack of the Metal Mites
The Duck Who Knew Too Much
Scrooge's Last Adventure
The Golden Goose part 1
The Golden Goose part 2

Note: Parts 1 and 2 of The Golden Goose are both full-length 22-minute episodes; however, part 2 is split into a sixteen-minute segment and a six-minute segment, so there are three video files called The Golden Goose. But they're all here.
